PREAMBLE

This License governs the use, reproduction, modification, and distribution
of NoteArmor Secured Notepad Pro (the "Software"), a privacy-first encrypted
text editor developed by PatronHubDevs Technologies.

The intent of this License is to:
  (a) Allow individuals to use the Software freely for personal, private,
      non-commercial purposes;
  (b) Protect the intellectual property and commercial interests of the Author;
  (c) Prevent exploitation of the Software in commercial products, services,
      or competitive offerings without explicit written authorization;
  (d) Preserve the integrity of the Software's identity and branding.

